- activity_log table: full SDK stream mirror (tool_use, text, subagent
  lifecycle) with parent_tool_use_id attribution; written from
  translateEvents, display-only, trimmed to 100 rows
- subagent spawn detected via Task/Agent tool_use; label from description;
  agent_done on matching tool_result
- renderer: >1 subagent → per-track lines (🔄/✅ + latest activity, old
  SubagentTrack UX); single track → ├/└ tree with 💬 text previews,
  <internal> markers stripped
- typing keepalive: processing_ack claim (age-bounded 30m) covers model
  thinking gaps between tools; tool_log kept for older container images
